# Ablo Marketing OS — learning ledger (append-only, git-tracked).
# The marketing-os-refresh agent reads this FIRST every run and writes to it LAST.
# This is how the OS compounds judgment over time: predict -> observe -> score -> distill.
#
# Two record types, one JSON object per line:
#
#  prediction  a falsifiable bet logged when you ship a fix or conclude an experiment.
#    {"type":"prediction","id":"PRED-YYYY-MM-DD-slug","date":"YYYY-MM-DD","action":"...",
#     "linked":"OS-... | PH-#### | CC-rank-N","metric":"<history.jsonl key>","baseline":N,
#     "predicted":N,"horizon_days":N,"due":"YYYY-MM-DD","rationale":"...","status":"open"}
#   when its horizon elapses, resolve it in place:
#     ...,"status":"resolved","actual":N,"verdict":"hit|partial|miss","resolved_date":"YYYY-MM-DD","lesson_id":"LES-..."
#
#  lesson  a durable heuristic distilled from a resolved bet or the weekly audit.
#    {"type":"lesson","id":"LES-YYYY-MM-DD-slug","date":"YYYY-MM-DD","lesson":"...",
#     "evidence":"...","confidence":"high|med|low","tags":["funnel","paid",...],"source_pred":"PRED-..."}
#
# Rules: never rewrite history except to resolve an open prediction. Keep lessons to one
# sentence, lead with the result, cite evidence. metric must be a real history.jsonl key.
