{"type":"lesson","id":"LES-2026-05-31-friction","date":"2026-05-31","lesson":"Removing auth friction at the signup step is the highest-ROI funnel move so far: Google-primary lifted completion 33% to 44% (+11pp).","evidence":"OS-SIGNUP-GOOGLE before/after; PRED-2026-05-20-google-signup resolved hit.","confidence":"high","tags":["funnel","signup","friction"],"source_pred":"PRED-2026-05-20-google-signup"}
